---
const certificates = [
  {
    image: '/assets/images/sijil/sijil%20halal%201.webp',
    alt: 'Sijil Halal JAKIM CUCKOO 1'
  },
  {
    image: '/assets/images/sijil/sijil%20halal%202.webp',
    alt: 'Sijil Halal JAKIM CUCKOO 2'
  },
  {
    image: '/assets/images/sijil/sijil%20halal%203.webp',
    alt: 'Sijil Halal JAKIM CUCKOO 3'
  }
];
---

<section id="halal-trust" class="bg-cream px-4 py-16 sm:px-6 lg:px-8">
  <div class="mx-auto max-w-7xl">
    <div class="grid min-w-0 gap-8 overflow-hidden rounded-[2rem] bg-white p-6 shadow-premium ring-1 ring-brand/10 lg:grid-cols-2 lg:items-center lg:p-10">
      
      <!-- LEFT: CERTIFICATE SWIPE -->
      <div class="min-w-0">
        <div class="flex min-w-0 snap-x gap-4 overflow-x-auto pb-5 [-ms-overflow-style:none] [scrollbar-width:none] [&::-webkit-scrollbar]:hidden">
          {certificates.map((item) => (
            <div class="w-full min-w-0 shrink-0 snap-center rounded-[1.5rem] bg-brand-cream p-4 shadow-soft ring-1 ring-brand/10 sm:p-5">
              <img
                src={item.image}
                alt={item.alt}
                loading="lazy"
                class="mx-auto h-[420px] w-full object-contain sm:h-[520px]"
              />
            </div>
          ))}
        </div>

        <p class="text-center text-xs font-bold text-brand-muted">
          Swipe kiri / kanan untuk lihat sijil lain
        </p>
      </div>

      <!-- RIGHT: TEXT -->
      <div class="lg:pl-6">
        <p class="text-sm font-black uppercase tracking-[.22em] text-brand-gold">
          Halal Compliance
        </p>

        <h2 class="mt-3 text-3xl font-black leading-tight text-brand-ink sm:text-4xl lg:text-5xl">
          Komited Memastikan Pematuhan Halal
        </h2>

        <p class="mt-5 text-base leading-8 text-brand-muted">
          Selaras dengan keperluan tempatan dan kepercayaan pelanggan daripada pelbagai latar belakang, CUCKOO komited dalam memastikan pematuhan Halal bagi produk dan perkhidmatan yang berkaitan.
        </p>

        <p class="mt-4 text-base leading-8 text-brand-muted">
          Penapis air CUCKOO telah mendapat pensijilan Halal daripada Jabatan Kemajuan Islam Malaysia (JAKIM). Pensijilan ini memberi keyakinan tambahan kepada pelanggan untuk penggunaan air minuman harian seisi keluarga.
        </p>

        <div class="mt-7 grid gap-3 sm:grid-cols-3">
          <div class="rounded-2xl bg-brand-cream p-4">
            <p class="font-black text-brand">Halal JAKIM</p>
            <p class="mt-1 text-sm text-brand-muted">Diiktiraf oleh pihak berautoriti.</p>
          </div>

          <div class="rounded-2xl bg-brand-cream p-4">
            <p class="font-black text-brand">Untuk Keluarga</p>
            <p class="mt-1 text-sm text-brand-muted">Lebih yakin untuk minuman harian.</p>
          </div>

          <div class="rounded-2xl bg-brand-cream p-4">
            <p class="font-black text-brand">Penapis Air CUCKOO</p>
            <p class="mt-1 text-sm text-brand-muted">Sesuai untuk rumah moden.</p>
          </div>
        </div>

        <p class="mt-5 text-xs leading-6 text-brand-muted">
          *Maklumat pensijilan tertakluk kepada dokumen rasmi dan kemas kini daripada pihak berkaitan.
        </p>
      </div>

    </div>
  </div>
</section>